title: American Horror Story Cult - Final Thoughts
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: This was my favorite season. I loved the characters, the focused storyline, and the horrifying realization that it gave Americans about our country. Evan peters deserves an Emmy for his amazing performance. I did like that there weren't supernatural aspects because I don't know how it would fit without. coming off as forced, especially since this season was more set in the real world. I have no idea how this season will be topped, but still very excited for next season.
This video was refreshing. I'm gonna miss cult. Kai was proabably one of my favorite characters in the show
